                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                                <locus from="2r" to="146v"/>
                                <title ref="LIT2000Mazmur"/>
                                <note>Each psalm is indicated with the same title: <foreign xml:lang="gez">መዝሙር፡ ለዳዊት፡ ሃሌሉያ፡</foreign>
                                    About four leaves with Psalm 49:2 up to 52:19 are missing between <locus target="#44"/> and <locus target="#45"/>.
                                    The numbering was added subsequently in a very careless manner. There are numerous errors, for example:
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">፭</foreign> instead of <foreign xml:lang="gez">፬</foreign> on <locus target="#21r"/>;
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">፻፩</foreign>, which was corrected to <foreign xml:lang="gez">፻፻፩</foreign>, instead of 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">፻፲፩</foreign> on <locus target="#112r"/> and many more. Often, the tens are written by 
                                    adding an <foreign xml:lang="gez">፲</foreign> to the preceding ten—for example, 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">፲፴</foreign> for <foreign xml:lang="gez">፵</foreign> on <locus target="#38r"/>, 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">፲፶</foreign> for <foreign xml:lang="gez">፷</foreign> on <locus target="#50v"/>, etc.
                                        </note>    
                            </msItem>
                            
